  "title": "Tom Holland confirms he and Zendaya are married",
  "description": "Tom Holland has apparently confirmed that he and his longtime love Zendaya have tied the knot, ending months of speculation triggered by Zendaya's stylist.",
  "text": "Looks like there’s a ring of truth to all the rumours about Tom Holland and Zendaya already being married. It’s no secret the couple, who met while starring in the Marvel film Spider-Man. Homecoming in 2016, were engaged. Zendaya was seen sporting a diamond ring at the Golden Globes in January 2025. But speculation the couple got married in secret was everywhere earlier this year after Zendaya’s longtime stylist, Law. Roach, told Access Hollywood on the Oscars red carpet that the wedding had already happened. In an interview published Tuesday, Holland seemingly confirmed to Esquire U.K. the two have now tied the knot. Shortly after Roach hinted that the wedding already happened, images generated by artificial intelligence started to appear online. Purporting to show the happy couple on their wedding day. Zendaya made it clear they were fake, even appearing on Jimmy Kimmel Live!",
